Nigel Clough and his players did not arrive at White Hart Lane until 40 minutes before the original kick-off time of 7.45pm, for Wednesday's game, which Spurs won 1-0.

The kick-off was delayed by 15 minutes and afterwards Clough said: 'It took us longer to do the five miles than it took us to get to London from Sheffield.' 

